d dumbbell: Dumbbell (connected-dot) plot comparing two time points by category
d
d Long-format input (category, two-valued time, value). Plots each category's
d two time points as markers joined by a line, sorted by one period's value.
d
d Requires: Stata 16 or newer.
d
d Author: Wen-Cheng Lin, Academia Sinica
d Source: https://github.com/ganma0517/stata_dumbbell
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260608
d
